Fast Company ranked us as the fourth most innovative company in the world this year.

144
00:14:53,677 --> 00:14:57,578
Time Magazine listed us among the most 100 influential companies.

145
00:14:59,359 --> 00:15:02,220
CNBC, 42nd most disruptive startup in the world.

146
00:15:02,280 --> 00:15:10,044
And we are recognized as a technical advisor with the Department of Energy and helping to advise folks on behalf of the Department of Energy on building electrification.

147
00:15:12,245 --> 00:15:15,346
And so with that, I'm going to pass it over to Dennis for what is electrification?

148
00:15:17,818 --> 00:15:18,299
