01:22:56,075 --> 01:22:56,776
All right, everyone.

784
01:22:56,816 --> 01:22:57,836
Have a great night.

785
01:22:57,897 --> 01:22:58,537
Thank you so much.

786
01:22:59,798 --> 01:23:00,178
Thank you.

787
01:23:00,218 --> 01:23:00,979
Have a great night.

788
01:23:01,379 --> 01:23:02,159
Thanks, everyone.

789
01:23:02,580 --> 01:23:02,880
Bye-bye.

